text: Emmanuel García Vaca (born December 28, 1989 in Zamora, Michoacán) is a Mexican footballer who currently plays as a left-back for club Pachuca. ==Career== On 8 December 2015, Tuzos de Pachuca announced that they had permanently signed 'Manny' from Veracruz. ==Honours== ===Club=== ;Pachuca * Liga MX: Clausura 2016 * CONCACAF Champions League: 2016–17 ==References== Category:1989 births Category:Living people Category:Footballers from Michoacán Category:People from Zamora, Michoacán Category:La Piedad footballers Category:C.D.
